User
    - username
    - firstname
    - lastname
    - password
    - email
    - avatar

Friend
    - userFirst
    - userSecond
    - type
    - chatID

ChatContent
    - User
    - content
    - date

MessagePrivate
    - ChatContent <many to many field>
    - chatID <primary key>


